711825f-a.title: Manhattan: 26th Street (East) - 3rd Avenue
711825f-a.text:
E. 26th Street, at the S. E. corner of Third Avenue, (right)
not shown). This modern apartment house was a drastic change from
the tenements from which it was reconstructed. Note in the fore-
ground a W. P. A. sewer project.
1936
C;ift of Committee on Housing
Charity Organization Society

708028f-a.title: Manhattan: 3rd Avenue - 26th Street (East)
708028f-a.text:
(1)
Third Ave., east side, north from East 26th Street, showing in the
background, (left to right) the Chanin and Chrysler Buildings. Also
seen is the 28th Street station of the Third Ave. Elevated Line.
December 23, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, from a point slightly northward.
December 23, 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
